HOW FAST DOES IT WORK? Early studies with the sensor have shown a diagnostic time between 1 and As we move forward, much of this scanning will be automated, making scanning even HOW DO I KNOW WHERE A STROKE MAY BE LOCATED? Tea tree oil, also known as melaleuca oil, is an essential oil that comes from steaming the leaves of the Australian tea Tea tree oil has been renowned for its broad spectrum antibacterial and antifungal How does Azuna work? Azuna is a low concentrate tea tree The delivery mechanism Azuna uses is through making the particles airborne rather than through droplets like in a high concentrate This allows for Azuna to absorb the mildew, bacteria, fungus, and odors from the room which it is placed in, rather than masking the issue like a diffuser or chemical based air For a quick how to video click HERE How long does Azuna last? The dissipation rate for Azuna will vary based upon conditions of the room but a good rule of thumb is to think of it as every ounce of Azuna covers sq feet for up to For example a 2 Azuna puck will last up to days in a sq ft Conditions that could increase the dissipation rate include, but are not limited to: Being placed near or directly under a fan Being placed in a room with heavy cigarette odors Being placed in a room with heavy pet odors What is the most effective way to use Azuna? Azuna can be placed anywhere in a room as long as it is on a flat If you are using Azuna for the first time it is recommended that you uncap the product and use without the lid for the first days to shock the After that place the lid back on to slow overall evaporation and enjoy the clean fresh air Azuna will provide you with for the next Is it toxic? What if my cat dog child ingested some? The Australian tea tree oil that Azuna uses is % natural and environmentally Research shows that tea tree oil is typically not toxic if it comes in to contact with the skin unless there is an underlying If ingested orally it is recommended that you see a doctor, but Azuna‚Äôs products are formulated as a low concentrate gel so that it should not cause any long term If you have ingested Azuna please call (800) How will I know when it is time to replace? Azuna will harden from its gel form as the bacteria is taken out of the air and into the After it hardens it is still effective for up to days before needing to Where is Azuna made? Azuna is made and shipped out of Buffalo, We are very proud to be able to make this amazing product in our hometown! Does Azuna really help with mold? It certainly For a demonstration visit our home page at and scroll down and view the ‚ÄúCheck Out The Azuna Difference!‚Äù How do I open the Azuna puck? Step 1: Unscrew lid and remove the inner seal Step 2: Screw lid back on and peel off sticker Step 3: Place in desired area and then get ready to breathe clean and clear air How do I get a subscription for the ‚ÄúWhole Home Kit‚Äù? Visit products home-starter-kit and click the subscription button and input how often you would like to receive What are the advantages to the ‚ÄúWhole Home Kit‚Äù? The Whole Home Kit provides you with enough of the Azuna tea tree gel to treat 4 rooms in your house for a year, which breaks down to a total cost of $8.25 per month, or $2.06 per room per If you purchase a subscription you will save an additional %. Is Azuna just for homes? Is it strong enough for the workplace? This is not an The brain is in constant communication with the gut, also known as the second brain, linking physiology to psychology, which is why it is common to hear, ‚ÄúI feel it in my gut!‚Äù. The communication path between the gut and brain ‚Äì The Axis (GBA) ‚Äì is key to maintaining good The GBA is influenced by the health of the gut and the brain and the bidirectional communication via the Central Nervous System (CNS), vagus nerve, and the Enteric Nervous System (ENS). standard of care Background As the population lives longer, neurodegenerative disorders such as mild cognitive impairment (MCI) and Alzheimer Disease (AD) become more There is a need for early identification and early treatment to enable delaying or halting of these progressive and debilitating disorders that start decades before symptomatic Unfortunately, there are no known methods to predict cognitive decline and the standard of care is defined by poorly sensitive subjective Vistim Labs seeks to address this need with convenient biomarkers to that predict and track cognitive decline in individuals such that early detection and monitoring is available for effective disease Objective At Vistim Labs, we seek to measure cognitive decline to enable measuring the efficacy of emerging treatments as they pertain to clinical We appreciate the difficulty of tracking neurodegenerative Measuring common biomarkers such amyloid deposits in the brain can be poor indicators of cognitive decline making them unsuitable for measuring efficacy of Vistim Labs believes that the ideal solution is a medical device that predicts known biophysiological biomarkers such as amyloid alongside changes in functional cognitive brain In this way, researchers and clinicians are best equipped to understand and stratify their patient Rationale In the case for Alzheimer‚Äôs Disease, Super Protocol Search this site Super Protocol Most data in the world is not completely secured There are three states that data could be in: at rest, in use, and in Traditionally data was secured only when stored (at rest) or being transferred across the network (in transit) thanks to encryption The same was not true for processing (in use). An unauthorized party could still access and tamper with data at This last shortcoming of data protection must be addressed to unlock the full value of data Confidential computing Confidential computing is the last puzzle piece in data By leveraging a trusted execution environment (TEE) it allows to isolate data during the Security of the TEE is based on embedded encryption keys and attestation mechanisms which guarantees that the keys could be used only by the authorized Intel SGX and AMD SEV technologies are two examples of the TEE Solution Super Protocol enables customers to superpower their data, algorithms and applications by providing a platform for active collaboration in an open, distributed and secure It is now possible to focus on innovation and finding synergy between vast amounts of data sources and bleeding edge technological solutions while the protocol takes care of sensitive data and intellectual property Benefits Unlock value of sensitive data without compromising security Innovate and collaborate while protecting your intellectual property Grow and scale your business with accessible computational resources Eliminate concerns when choosing cloud providers Our Projects Data collaborations: Business ecosystems, Marketing and ad management, Value chain optimization, Researches, Market analytics and benchmarking Joint data modeling, analytics, marketing campaigns and loyalty programs Audience management, advanced ML models, analytics, BI, loyalty management Secure joint calculations Top independent retailers, telco, banks with total audience more than people are working on the platform for their advertisement management, cross sales, data monetization, risk management and other scenarios New York Report abuse Page details Page updated Google Sites Report abuse
